description:
The Vampire Diaries: Slipping Underneath (Kindle Worlds) (The Doppelganger Diaries) by Jessica Smith


It was well-known that vampires couldn't procreate, not with humans nor other vampires. Many had tried and none had succeeded. So when, after an intimate night together with Stefan Salvatore, Elena Gilbert ends up pregnant, a lot of questions are posed. Can the baby really be Stefan's? And if so, what does that mean about Elena? In the quest for these answers, relationships are tested and lives are put on the line as Elena turns to Stefan's infamous brother, Damon, for the help she needs.



Genre: Romance | Fantasy
